1
00:01:00,560 --> 00:01:01,760
I used to dream

2
00:01:02,800 --> 00:01:04,459
of standing on stage with you.

3
00:01:05,640 --> 00:01:07,440
Then with Fengming, I just hoped

4
00:01:08,640 --> 00:01:10,600
you two would remain on stage.

5
00:01:12,360 --> 00:01:13,600
But this opera,

6
00:01:14,360 --> 00:01:15,560
without you now,

7
00:01:17,720 --> 00:01:19,640
isn't an opera anymore.

8
00:01:30,280 --> 00:01:31,280
Don't be afraid.

9
00:01:32,680 --> 00:01:33,920
After tomorrow,

10
00:01:35,440 --> 00:01:37,570
when Jiupu takes Fengming to Beiping,

11
00:01:40,000 --> 00:01:41,520
I'll come join you.

12
00:01:45,479 --> 00:01:47,280
I used to dream of this day.

13
00:01:47,640 --> 00:01:49,479
Now men and women can actually share the stage.

14
00:01:49,479 --> 00:01:50,810
I can hardly believe it.

15
00:01:51,400 --> 00:01:52,330
It's wonderful.

16
00:01:52,800 --> 00:01:55,520
In the future, we'll perform plays we wrote ourselves.

17
00:01:55,520 --> 00:01:57,850
We'll sing them to the audience together.

18
00:01:59,200 --> 00:02:00,460
Is this news reliable?

19
00:02:01,640 --> 00:02:02,480
Don't be like before.

20
00:02:02,480 --> 00:02:04,400
Everyone outside is talking about it.

21
00:02:04,400 --> 00:02:06,800
You're just acting like a frightened bird.

22
00:02:08,120 --> 00:02:09,280
Do you remember that one time

23
00:02:09,280 --> 00:02:10,759
we sang "Farewell My Concubine"

24
00:02:10,759 --> 00:02:12,160
and got caught by the old troupe master?

25
00:02:12,160 --> 00:02:14,360
He sprayed tea dregs all over your face.

26
00:02:14,360 --> 00:02:15,040
From now on,

27
00:02:15,200 --> 00:02:17,000
we won't sing "Farewell My Concubine"

28
00:02:17,000 --> 00:02:18,560
or perform "The Butterfly Lovers".

29
00:02:18,560 --> 00:02:20,079
We'll just sing about Jin Guizhi

30
00:02:20,079 --> 00:02:21,520
and Yun Feiyan.

31
00:02:24,360 --> 00:02:25,440
I thought of a name.

32
00:02:29,040 --> 00:02:29,720
Fu

33
00:02:31,280 --> 00:02:31,880
Sheng.

34
00:02:39,240 --> 00:02:40,400
Life

35
00:02:41,000 --> 00:02:42,240
is a

36
00:02:42,400 --> 00:02:43,120
dream.

37
00:02:47,840 --> 00:02:50,960
Makeup hides the brows.

38
00:02:52,200 --> 00:02:57,400
Water sleeves hide the beauty.

39
00:02:58,520 --> 00:02:59,040
Great.

40
00:02:59,040 --> 00:03:00,100
That line is great.

41
00:03:08,360 --> 00:03:09,240
The

42
00:03:09,760 --> 00:03:10,440
brows.

43
00:03:14,600 --> 00:03:15,880
Hide.

44
00:03:16,600 --> 00:03:17,840
The

45
00:03:19,160 --> 00:03:20,280
beauty.

46
00:03:27,000 --> 00:03:28,040
Senior Sister.

47
00:03:29,079 --> 00:03:31,480
Senior Sister was kicked out of the troupe.

48
00:03:31,800 --> 00:03:32,880
When did this happen?

49
00:03:32,880 --> 00:03:33,920
Why didn't I know?

50
00:03:35,079 --> 00:03:37,680
Senior Sister had an affair with a man outside,

51
00:03:37,920 --> 00:03:39,480
and got pregnant.

52
00:03:39,680 --> 00:03:41,140
She was afraid to tell you,

53
00:03:41,280 --> 00:03:43,920
so she asked me to secretly buy abortion powder.

54
00:03:43,920 --> 00:03:45,680
But Manager Cui found out,

55
00:03:46,120 --> 00:03:47,980
so he kicked her out of the troupe.

56
00:03:48,640 --> 00:03:49,640
Senior Brother.

57
00:03:49,640 --> 00:03:52,079
Senior Sister said she's too ashamed to see you.

58
00:03:52,079 --> 00:03:53,960
She asked you not to look for her.

59
00:03:58,200 --> 00:04:00,240
I know what kind of person Jin Guizhi is

60
00:04:00,240 --> 00:04:01,800
better than you do.

61
00:04:02,720 --> 00:04:03,680
Don't let me hear

62
00:04:03,800 --> 00:04:05,130
that kind of talk again.

63
00:04:05,520 --> 00:04:07,250
Otherwise, no matter who it is,

64
00:04:07,560 --> 00:04:08,800
I won't spare them.

65
00:04:57,159 --> 00:04:58,220
You're back, Miss.

66
00:04:58,280 --> 00:04:59,640
I'll have someone prepare a meal for you.

67
00:04:59,640 --> 00:05:00,600
No need, Tian.

68
00:05:00,840 --> 00:05:01,970
I've already eaten.

69
00:05:05,360 --> 00:05:06,920
Master was invited out for drinks.

70
00:05:06,920 --> 00:05:08,360
He should be back soon.

71
00:05:10,040 --> 00:05:10,920
Okay.

72
00:06:54,280 --> 00:06:55,480
Put the flowers here.

73
00:06:56,960 --> 00:06:58,090
Hurry up, everyone.

74
00:06:59,200 --> 00:06:59,880
Please.

75
00:07:28,800 --> 00:07:30,680
Are you getting old?

76
00:07:31,280 --> 00:07:33,080
You're always nagging.

77
00:07:33,080 --> 00:07:34,360
It's annoying.

78
00:07:34,480 --> 00:07:35,940
So what if I drink a little?

79
00:07:47,040 --> 00:07:48,080
I thought

80
00:07:48,400 --> 00:07:51,080
you'd forgotten about your father.

81
00:07:54,200 --> 00:07:55,080
Miss.

82
00:08:00,040 --> 00:08:01,360
I have work at the police station.

83
00:08:01,360 --> 00:08:02,240
I'm leaving.

84
00:08:03,920 --> 00:08:04,920
Stop right there.

85
00:08:07,080 --> 00:08:09,440
You haven't been home in sixteen years.

86
00:08:09,520 --> 00:08:11,450
Do you really think this is a hotel?

87
00:08:13,280 --> 00:08:16,000
I spent a fortune sending you to France,

88
00:08:17,600 --> 00:08:19,760
not so you could come back and be a cop.

89
00:08:26,440 --> 00:08:28,920
You show your face in public all day.

90
00:08:28,920 --> 00:08:29,760
Who you've offended,

91
00:08:29,760 --> 00:08:30,890
you don't even know.

92
00:08:33,640 --> 00:08:35,240
You didn't let me join the police station

93
00:08:35,240 --> 00:08:36,440
because you feared I'd offend people,

94
00:08:36,440 --> 00:08:37,360
cut off their income,

95
00:08:37,360 --> 00:08:38,690
and hurt your business.

96
00:08:39,360 --> 00:08:40,760
You're still so selfish.

97
00:08:41,120 --> 00:08:42,850
You only think about yourself.

98
00:08:43,600 --> 00:08:44,280
You...

99
00:08:44,760 --> 00:08:46,690
who do you think you're talking to?

100
00:08:48,840 --> 00:08:50,760
You think this is integrity?

101
00:08:52,120 --> 00:08:53,480
It's stupidity.

102
00:08:56,120 --> 00:08:57,880
You're making a mess for me.

103
00:08:58,640 --> 00:09:00,400
If the laws of the Concession

104
00:09:00,440 --> 00:09:02,920
only protect powerful people like you,

105
00:09:03,320 --> 00:09:04,680
Then what's the point?

106
00:09:04,960 --> 00:09:05,920
I didn't join the police force

107
00:09:05,920 --> 00:09:08,040
to cover up for the Lin family.

108
00:09:08,440 --> 00:09:09,320
There are too many people

109
00:09:09,320 --> 00:09:10,120
who need the truth,

110
00:09:10,120 --> 00:09:11,160
who need justice.

111
00:09:11,400 --> 00:09:12,200
Justice?

112
00:09:17,000 --> 00:09:18,760
Do you really think what you learned in France

113
00:09:18,760 --> 00:09:20,760
is actually useful?

114
00:09:22,040 --> 00:09:24,040
Do you think you became Inspector

115
00:09:24,520 --> 00:09:26,000
on your own?

116
00:09:26,200 --> 00:09:28,000
Do you think anyone would take

117
00:09:28,480 --> 00:09:30,480
a Chinese woman like you seriously?

118
00:09:30,680 --> 00:09:31,680
All of this,

119
00:09:33,400 --> 00:09:34,920
I gave it to you.

120
00:09:38,760 --> 00:09:40,440
The police station is no place for you.

121
00:09:40,440 --> 00:09:42,640
The son of an old family friend in Suzhou

122
00:09:42,760 --> 00:09:44,560
is coming to Shanghai tomorrow.

123
00:09:45,000 --> 00:09:45,960
Go and meet him.

124
00:09:47,800 --> 00:09:48,680
If this is the only way

125
00:09:48,680 --> 00:09:50,400
you can feel like a father,

126
00:09:52,080 --> 00:09:53,140
then don't bother.

127
00:09:56,720 --> 00:09:58,200
I don't need you to decide

128
00:09:58,240 --> 00:09:59,160
what I can do.

129
00:09:59,680 --> 00:10:01,940
And I don't need you to decide who I marry.

130
00:10:02,720 --> 00:10:04,380
I make the rules in this house.

131
00:10:05,320 --> 00:10:06,480
Tomorrow at 12:00 PM.

132
00:10:06,480 --> 00:10:07,280
Huixin Tower.

133
00:10:08,200 --> 00:10:09,880
The butler will take you there.

134
00:10:09,880 --> 00:10:10,920
His name is

135
00:10:11,560 --> 00:10:12,680
Yu Jiupu.

136
00:10:22,040 --> 00:10:22,440
Are you from

137
00:10:22,440 --> 00:10:23,570
the police station?

138
00:10:26,080 --> 00:10:27,960
We need to conduct a thorough search.

139
00:10:27,960 --> 00:10:29,360
I hope you'll cooperate.

140
00:10:50,880 --> 00:10:51,720
Miss Jin,

141
00:10:51,960 --> 00:10:53,690
we're from the police station.

142
00:11:14,520 --> 00:11:16,780
You're here to see my mother, aren't you?

143
00:11:17,520 --> 00:11:18,720
At this hour,

144
00:11:18,920 --> 00:11:20,720
she should be in the prayer room.

145
00:11:22,440 --> 00:11:23,760
You are Jin Fengming.

146
00:11:24,280 --> 00:11:25,920
I saw you here yesterday.

147
00:11:26,320 --> 00:11:27,520
If you need anything,

148
00:11:27,680 --> 00:11:28,600
you can ask me.

149
00:11:30,320 --> 00:11:32,200
I heard that after this opera,

150
00:11:32,480 --> 00:11:33,880
you're going to Beiping.

151
00:11:34,600 --> 00:11:35,800
Shanghai is big,

152
00:11:36,400 --> 00:11:37,730
but it has no room for me.

153
00:11:38,080 --> 00:11:39,880
Might as well go somewhere else.

154
00:11:41,360 --> 00:11:42,690
Beiping is a good place.

155
00:11:42,840 --> 00:11:44,900
Will you still sing opera in Beiping?

156
00:11:45,400 --> 00:11:47,400
If someone sets up the stage, I'll sing.

157
00:11:47,400 --> 00:11:48,920
If not, I won't.

158
00:11:49,680 --> 00:11:51,010
Besides singing opera,

159
00:11:51,240 --> 00:11:53,100
there are many other things to do.

160
00:11:54,600 --> 00:11:57,000
Yu Jiupu must have already set up the stage.

161
00:11:57,400 --> 00:11:58,400
If you don't sing,

162
00:11:58,640 --> 00:12:00,240
I'm afraid he won't be happy.

163
00:12:01,000 --> 00:12:02,360
He doesn't understand opera,

164
00:12:02,360 --> 00:12:03,890
nor is he part of that world.

165
00:12:04,960 --> 00:12:06,160
Unlike my mother,

166
00:12:06,840 --> 00:12:09,080
who can't distinguish the play from reality.

167
00:12:09,080 --> 00:12:10,720
She doesn't know if she's dreaming

168
00:12:10,720 --> 00:12:11,760
or awake.

169
00:12:41,680 --> 00:12:42,800
Boss Yun is gone.

170
00:12:43,800 --> 00:12:45,360
I knew this day would come.

171
00:12:47,320 --> 00:12:48,960
But Fengming is all grown up.

172
00:12:49,360 --> 00:12:50,480
It's time he knew.

173
00:12:54,240 --> 00:12:56,080
How did you meet Yu Jiupu?

174
00:12:56,080 --> 00:12:57,540
He came to the opera often,

175
00:12:58,080 --> 00:13:00,140
so we got to know each other over time.

176
00:13:01,680 --> 00:13:03,440
On July 7, 16 years ago,

177
00:13:04,280 --> 00:13:06,800
two opium addicts dragged me into an opium den and assaulted me.

178
00:13:06,800 --> 00:13:07,520
This...

179
00:13:08,560 --> 00:13:10,890
is where they burned me with an opium pipe.

180
00:13:12,800 --> 00:13:13,880
Where is he now?

181
00:13:14,600 --> 00:13:16,120
He should be in Peiping.

182
00:13:18,640 --> 00:13:20,570
I'll go check if my mother is ready.

183
00:13:21,600 --> 00:13:22,640
Jin Guizhi.

184
00:13:29,080 --> 00:13:30,520
I kept wondering

185
00:13:31,200 --> 00:13:32,880
why it was you and Yu Jiupu.

186
00:13:34,920 --> 00:13:36,360
Now I understand.

187
00:13:51,120 --> 00:13:52,200
Tomorrow at 12 p.m.

188
00:13:52,280 --> 00:13:53,410
Huixin Restaurant.

189
00:13:54,480 --> 00:13:55,520
His name is

190
00:13:56,160 --> 00:13:57,280
Yu Jiupu.

191
00:14:00,560 --> 00:14:01,520
You said yesterday

192
00:14:01,520 --> 00:14:03,920
that you wanted us to clear Boss Yun's name.

193
00:14:04,480 --> 00:14:06,410
We found blood not belonging to her

194
00:14:06,640 --> 00:14:08,770
on the soles of Xiaotangchun's shoes.

195
00:14:08,960 --> 00:14:10,320
But to confirm it,

196
00:14:10,760 --> 00:14:12,480
we need Boss Yun's body

197
00:14:12,720 --> 00:14:14,120
to do a blood comparison.

198
00:14:15,040 --> 00:14:16,570
It doesn't matter anymore.

199
00:14:16,920 --> 00:14:18,280
That person has already admitted everything

200
00:14:18,280 --> 00:14:19,410
right in front of me.

201
00:14:20,640 --> 00:14:21,920
I have avenged

202
00:14:23,000 --> 00:14:24,120
Boss Yun.

203
00:14:38,280 --> 00:14:39,210
Senior Brother.

204
00:14:39,840 --> 00:14:41,240
I didn't want to kill you.

205
00:14:41,280 --> 00:14:42,920
I didn't want to kill you.

206
00:14:42,920 --> 00:14:43,600
I'm sorry.

207
00:14:43,600 --> 00:14:44,360
I was wrong.

208
00:14:44,360 --> 00:14:45,040
I'm sorry.

209
00:14:45,640 --> 00:14:47,040
Look at yourself.

210
00:14:47,440 --> 00:14:48,800
Just for a play?

211
00:14:49,600 --> 00:14:50,680
To become a star?

212
00:14:52,040 --> 00:14:53,200
Is it worth it?

213
00:15:01,280 --> 00:15:02,480
Is it worth it?

214
00:15:04,000 --> 00:15:05,000
Is it worth it?

215
00:15:08,920 --> 00:15:10,520
You forced me.

216
00:15:12,120 --> 00:15:13,760
When Jin Guizhi was here,

217
00:15:14,800 --> 00:15:16,600
you wouldn't even look at me.

218
00:15:17,400 --> 00:15:19,000
Now that she's finally gone,

219
00:15:19,320 --> 00:15:20,120
you'd rather change the script

220
00:15:20,120 --> 00:15:21,880
than let me play the lead.

221
00:15:22,920 --> 00:15:24,320
Why didn't you just

222
00:15:24,320 --> 00:15:26,120
give the theater to me?

223
00:15:27,040 --> 00:15:28,440
Why did you push me?

224
00:15:29,040 --> 00:15:29,760
Why?

225
00:15:31,880 --> 00:15:32,640
Why?

226
00:15:33,120 --> 00:15:34,200
Why?

227
00:15:34,680 --> 00:15:35,960
You'll never be a star.

228
00:15:37,720 --> 00:15:39,200
You never will be.

229
00:15:40,840 --> 00:15:42,170
You weren't one before.

230
00:15:42,840 --> 00:15:44,600
And never will be.

231
00:15:46,240 --> 00:15:47,920
You forced me.

232
00:15:49,080 --> 00:15:49,880
Originally,

233
00:15:50,200 --> 00:15:52,680
you just had to wait for the drug to take effect,

234
00:15:52,680 --> 00:15:55,720
and Xiaotangchun would die of organ failure.

235
00:15:55,960 --> 00:15:57,720
But something went wrong.

236
00:15:58,520 --> 00:15:59,920
Because of Jin Fengming.

237
00:16:00,280 --> 00:16:01,080
Right?

238
00:16:08,600 --> 00:16:09,600
I'm sorry.

239
00:16:10,080 --> 00:16:11,540
This place is hard to find.

240
00:16:22,760 --> 00:16:24,360
I thought you wouldn't come.

241
00:16:26,000 --> 00:16:27,400
My father told me

242
00:16:27,760 --> 00:16:30,160
you're an inspector at the Police Station.

243
00:16:30,160 --> 00:16:31,020
I've never seen

244
00:16:31,720 --> 00:16:33,280
a female inspector before.

245
00:16:34,480 --> 00:16:37,410
So I asked my father to arrange this meeting with you.

246
00:16:40,840 --> 00:16:42,760
We just saw each other yesterday.

247
00:16:44,520 --> 00:16:45,160
Besides,

248
00:16:46,040 --> 00:16:48,170
shouldn't you be in Beiping right now?

249
00:16:56,080 --> 00:16:57,340
I brought this for you.

250
00:16:58,000 --> 00:16:59,440
If you have time,

251
00:17:00,200 --> 00:17:01,480
you can go watch it

252
00:17:02,800 --> 00:17:03,800
with your friend.

253
00:17:05,359 --> 00:17:06,490
What a coincidence.

254
00:17:07,119 --> 00:17:08,760
I have something for you too.

255
00:17:09,760 --> 00:17:11,240
I heard it's custom-made.

256
00:17:12,960 --> 00:17:14,760
It'll be hard to replace if lost.

257
00:17:15,160 --> 00:17:17,020
Plus, your clothes are borrowed.

258
00:17:17,319 --> 00:17:20,050
I'm afraid you'll have a hard time explaining it.

259
00:17:21,520 --> 00:17:22,720
Stop wasting time.

260
00:17:24,359 --> 00:17:26,680
Tell me everything you know.

261
00:17:27,599 --> 00:17:29,120
Jin Fengming is dead.

262
00:17:30,760 --> 00:17:31,560
Right?

263
00:17:32,000 --> 00:17:33,600
Fengming is still a child.

264
00:17:35,120 --> 00:17:36,680
She has someone she loves.

265
00:17:38,000 --> 00:17:40,330
There are still many places you want to go.

266
00:17:43,640 --> 00:17:45,080
After you finish this opera,

267
00:17:45,080 --> 00:17:46,360
you can go wherever you want.

268
00:17:46,360 --> 00:17:47,360
I won't stop you.

269
00:17:48,200 --> 00:17:48,880
Mom.

270
00:17:49,520 --> 00:17:51,160
Is this opera

271
00:17:51,280 --> 00:17:52,940
really that important to you?

272
00:17:54,880 --> 00:17:56,610
Boss Yun and I waited a lifetime

273
00:17:56,640 --> 00:17:58,640
for this 'Dream of a Floating Life',

274
00:17:59,280 --> 00:18:00,680
but never finished it.

275
00:18:02,080 --> 00:18:04,140
You're fulfilling this wish for her.

276
00:18:04,720 --> 00:18:06,160
It's what we owe her.

277
00:18:08,480 --> 00:18:09,280
Mom.

278
00:18:09,960 --> 00:18:11,320
Whose child am I?

279
00:18:13,640 --> 00:18:14,640
Remember this.

280
00:18:15,520 --> 00:18:17,120
You owe your life to Boss Yun.

281
00:18:17,600 --> 00:18:19,480
You are his child and mine.

282
00:18:20,200 --> 00:18:21,360
That night,

283
00:18:22,040 --> 00:18:23,240
Fengming promised me

284
00:18:24,120 --> 00:18:25,920
that after the show the next day,

285
00:18:26,720 --> 00:18:28,320
we'd go to Beiping together.

286
00:18:29,440 --> 00:18:31,440
I queued overnight for the tickets.

287
00:18:46,000 --> 00:18:47,120
Fengming.

288
00:18:58,280 --> 00:18:59,520
I don't remember

289
00:19:01,040 --> 00:19:02,900
how long I held Fengming that day.

290
00:19:03,400 --> 00:19:04,960
Later, Jin Guizhi found me.

291
00:19:05,600 --> 00:19:06,760
We agreed

292
00:19:07,000 --> 00:19:08,920
the show would go on the next day.

293
00:19:09,320 --> 00:19:10,780
Not only would we perform,

294
00:19:11,960 --> 00:19:13,420
we also put it in the paper.

295
00:19:13,840 --> 00:19:15,880
We thought if the killer saw it,

296
00:19:16,240 --> 00:19:18,040
he'd surely come to check it out.

297
00:19:19,960 --> 00:19:21,090
That day, Jin Guizhi

298
00:19:22,160 --> 00:19:23,680
dressed up as Fengming

299
00:19:25,440 --> 00:19:26,570
to perform on stage.

300
00:19:27,400 --> 00:19:28,600
I was in the audience,

301
00:19:29,800 --> 00:19:31,800
watching for suspicious behavior.

302
00:19:41,560 --> 00:19:42,680
Impossible.

303
00:19:42,680 --> 00:19:44,040
She's dead.

304
00:19:44,960 --> 00:19:46,200
She clearly died.
